OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright spells and blustery
OL,6,Fshowers at first. Drier for a time in
OL,7,Fthe middle of the day before further
OL,8,Fshowers later, heavy at times. Cool
OL,9,Fand blustery.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FScattered to frequent
OL,12,Fblustery showers feed in from the west
OL,13,Fthrough the evening and overnight,
OL,14,Fthese showers heavy at times. Chance
OL,15,Fof frost developing in places.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FIt will be quite cool with
OL,18,Fbright or sunny spells and scattered
OL,19,Fheavy showers. Chance of overnight
OL,20,Ffrost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
